{"_id":"0XiOPuoCmJ8VhUPH","name":"Metamagic: Twinned Spell","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-blue.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.Qb391hakCfmH4w8p"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you cast a spell that targets only one creature and doesn't have a range of self, you can spend a number of sorcery points equal to the spell's level to target a second creature in range with the same spell (1 sorcery point if the spell is a cantrip).</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Foundry Note: Once adding this to a sheet, you will need to tell it what resource to consume when used.</p>\n<p>When casting Twinned Spell with a spell level higher than one, you will have to manually input the number of Sorcery Points consumed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"W&W p.10","activation":{"type":"special","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"Casting Style 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.2","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1662995424784,"modifiedTime":1662995424913,"lastModifiedBy":"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if"}}
{"_id":"2XpSvO76HrbQI3RA","name":"Metamagic: Extended Spell","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/time/hourglass-yellow-green.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.tQxlKyAx9sgPrbgj"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you cast a spell that has a duration of 1 minute or longer, you can spend 1 sorcery point to double its duration, to a maximum duration of 24 hours.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Foundry Note: Once adding this to a sheet, you will need to tell it what resource to consume when used.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"W&W p.10","activation":{"type":"special","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"Casting Style 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.2","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1662995424822,"modifiedTime":1662995424941,"lastModifiedBy":"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if"}}
{"_id":"2zmeq5HSeaM5RzwR","name":"Metamagic: Heightened Spell","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/fire/explosion-mushroom-nuke-orange.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.tNG2qi9zhmXEkecA"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you cast a spell that forces a creature to make a saving throw to resist its effects, you can spend 3 sorcery points to give one target of the spell disadvantage on its first saving throw made against the spell.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Foundry Note: Once adding this to a sheet, you will need to tell it what resource to consume when used.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"W&W p.10","activation":{"type":"special","cost":3,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":3},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"Casting Style 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.2","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1662995424826,"modifiedTime":1662995424951,"lastModifiedBy":"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if"}}
{"_id":"53o6GUyTl5v6fGAw","name":"Metamagic: Careful Spell","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/nature/beam-hand-leaves-green.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.zElYrOcCFFMhB6Xl"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you cast a spell that forces other creatures to make a saving throw, you can protect some of those creatures from the spell's full force. To do so, you spend 1 sorcery point and choose a number of those creatures up to your Charisma modifier (minimum of one creature). A chosen creature automatically succeeds on its saving throw against the spell.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Foundry Note: Once adding this to a sheet you will need to tell it where to consume uses.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"W&W p.10","activation":{"type":"special","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"Casting Style 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.2","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1662995424829,"modifiedTime":1662995424970,"lastModifiedBy":"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if"}}
{"_id":"AOBBrCnhIt4wNWEP","name":"Metamagic: Distant Spell","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/targeting/target-strike-triple-blue.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.DZpAa3LzMNBexbmX"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you cast a spell that has a range of 5 feet or greater, you can spend 1 sorcery point to double the range of the spell.</p>\n<p>When you cast a spell that has a range of touch, you can spend 1 sorcery point to make the range of the spell 30 feet.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Foundry Note: Once adding this to a sheet, you will need to tell it what resource to consume when used.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"W&W p.10","activation":{"type":"special","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"Casting Style 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.2","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1662995424833,"modifiedTime":1662995424984,"lastModifiedBy":"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if"}}
{"_id":"HVuYc7tKoVykdW8k","name":"Metamagic: Resistant Spell","type":"feat","img":"icons/equipment/shield/buckler-wooden-boss-glowing-blue.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, when you cast a spell, you can spend 1 sorcery point per increased level to make spell deflection, @Compendium[wands.spells-wands.SQnurPdikw1UbJ3p]{Finite Incantatem}, or @Compendium[wands.spells-wands.F65nsK2xlfBqNOhH]{Reparifors}  as if your spell was cast using a spell slot higher than its original level, making your spell more resistant. The spell's higher level cannot exceed your highest available level of spell slots. This does not count against your number of Metamagic options.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Foundry Note: Once adding this to a sheet, you will need to tell it what resource to consume when used.</p>\n<p>When casting Resistant Spell with an increased spell level, you will have to manually input the number of Sorcery Points consumed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"W&W p.11","activation":{"type":"special","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":1},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Willpower Caster 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.2","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1662995424837,"modifiedTime":1662995424997,"lastModifiedBy":"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if"}}
{"_id":"JKsqMhcQtgRVUsBD","name":"Metamagic","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/unholy/orb-colllecting-energy-green.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.9Uh7uTDNZ04oTJsL"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, you gain the ability to twist your spells to suit your needs. You gain two of the following Metamagic options of your choice. You gain another one at 10th and 17th level. You can use only one Metamagic option on a spell when you cast it, unless otherwise noted.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[wands.metamagic-wands.53o6GUyTl5v6fGAw]{Careful Spell}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[wands.metamagic-wands.AOBBrCnhIt4wNWEP]{Distant Spell}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[wands.metamagic-wands.zSGuBxxzMPNOaeaf]{Empowered Spell}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[wands.metamagic-wands.2XpSvO76HrbQI3RA]{Extended Spell}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[wands.metamagic-wands.2zmeq5HSeaM5RzwR]{Heightened Spell}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[wands.metamagic-wands.RivETuE81DWUcsH8]{Quickened Spell}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[wands.metamagic-wands.Tw6ts854vuUpMmOt]{Subtle Spell}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[wands.metamagic-wands.0XiOPuoCmJ8VhUPH]{Twinned Spell}</p>\n<p>You can drag your choices from the above onto your character sheet and it will automatically update.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"W&W p.10","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":"","long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"Casting Style 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"featType":{"value":"passive","_deprecated":true,"type":"String","label":"Feat Type"},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true}},"ownership":{"default":0,"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.2","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1662995424844,"modifiedTime":1662995425006,"lastModifiedBy":"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if"}}
{"_id":"PSOeU9xdUlBCXDWw","name":"Metamagic: Fierce Spell","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-glow-yellow.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, when you cast a spell, you can spend 2 sorcery points to cast that spell as if it were cast using a spell slot one level higher than its original level, or 4 sorcery points to cast that spell two levels higher. The spell's higher level cannot exceed your highest available level of spell slots. This does not count against your number of Metamagic options.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Foundry Note: Once adding this to a sheet, you will need to tell it what resource to consume when used.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"W&W p.11","activation":{"type":"special","cost":2,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":2},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Willpower Caster 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.2","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1662995424848,"modifiedTime":1662995425014,"lastModifiedBy":"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if"}}
{"_id":"RivETuE81DWUcsH8","name":"Metamagic: Quickened Spell","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/time/clock-stopwatch-white-blue.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.nViGf6bZ6DQAJhkw"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you cast a spell that has a casting time of 1 action, you can spend 2 sorcery points to change the casting time to 1 bonus action for this casting.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Foundry Note: Once adding this to a sheet, you will need to tell it what resource to consume when used.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"W&W p.10","activation":{"type":"special","cost":2,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":2},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Casting Style 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.2","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1662995424851,"modifiedTime":1662995425022,"lastModifiedBy":"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if"}}
{"name":"Font of Magic","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/control/silhouette-hold-change-blue.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.LBKChJY5n02Afhnq"}},"_id":"S8XO84aQCrIwMYsE","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 2nd level, you tap into a deep wellspring of magic within yourself. This wellspring is represented by sorcery points, which allow you to create a variety of magical effects.</p>\n<h3>Sorcery Points</h3>\n<p>You can never have more sorcery points than your level dictates.  You regain all spent sorcery points when you finish a long rest.</p>\n<h3>Flexible Casting</h3>\n<p>You can use your sorcery points to gain additional spell slots, or sacrifice spell slots to gain additional sorcery points. You learn other ways to use your sorcery points as you reach higher levels.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Creating Spell Slots</strong>.</em>You can transform unexpended sorcery points into one spell slot as a bonus action on your turn. The Creating Spell Slots table shows the cost of creating a spell slot of a given level. You can create spell slots no higher in level than 5th.</p>\n<p>Any spell slot you create with this feature vanishes when you finish a long rest.</p>\n<table border=\"1\"><caption>Creating Spell Slots</caption>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Spell Slot Level</strong></td>\n<td><strong>Sorcery Point Cost</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2nd</td>\n<td>3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4th</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>7</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><em><strong>Converting a Spell Slot to Sorcery Points</strong>.</em>As a bonus action on your turn, you can expend one spell slot and gain a number of sorcery points equal to the slot's level.</p>\n<p><em>**Foundry note:</em><em>Use this to track all the various uses of sorcery points for the spell caster.</em><em> Please manually adjust as required.</em></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"W&W p.10","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"lr","type":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"Casting Style 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.2","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1662995424854,"modifiedTime":1662995425032,"lastModifiedBy":"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if"}}
{"_id":"Tw6ts854vuUpMmOt","name":"Metamagic: Subtle Spell","type":"feat","img":"icons/creatures/slimes/slime-movement-swirling-blue.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.fXa0DMhoVLtbBu9l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you cast a spell, you can spend 1 sorcery point to cast it without any somatic or verbal components.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Foundry Note: Once adding this to a sheet, you will need to tell it what resource to consume when used.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"W&W p.10","activation":{"type":"special","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"Casting Style 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.2","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1662995424858,"modifiedTime":1662995425040,"lastModifiedBy":"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if"}}
{"_id":"zSGuBxxzMPNOaeaf","name":"Metamagic: Empowered Spell","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/air/wind-tornado-wall-blue.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.IWpe0Y9uAStHGiH1"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you roll damage for a spell, you can spend 1 sorcery point to reroll a number of the damage dice up to your spellcasting ability modifier (minimum of one). You must use the new rolls.</p>\n<p>You can use Empowered Spell even if you have already used a different Metamagic option during the casting of the spell.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Foundry Note: Once adding this to a sheet, you will need to tell it what resource to consume when used.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"W&W p.10","activation":{"type":"special","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"Casting Style 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.2","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1662995424862,"modifiedTime":1662995425049,"lastModifiedBy":"6KPKvdrxQhprt6if"}}
